(EXAMINEFILES
  [LAMBDA (FILE1 FILE2 TITLE1 TITLE2 REGION)                 (* ; "Edited  1-Feb-2022 23:15 by rmk")
                                                             (* ; "Edited 25-Jan-2022 10:08 by rmk")
